metadata.name: Bee Free
metadata.description:
Disclaimer: Title is intentionally punned.

I know times can be hard mentally, emotionally, and physically in life. It's important to break free from our negative thoughts that may appear in our minds, and try to keep us trapped in a cycle of sadness. Don't give into the pressure of life or bad influences. Work with who loves you the most. Yourself. Your heart. Your friends. 

Dimensions: 3000 x4200 px
300 DPI

Collectors and Bidders will receive Thank You drawing. 
Collector will receive surprise drawing.
